title: Star Trek Klingon Academy
description:
Star Trek Klingon Academy - PC CD
-------------------------

This is the full game, all 6 CDs.

Have also included Virtual CloneDrive to read the ISO disk images as not a standard format, though I'm sure there are other programs out there that can read .img files.

Runs for me without setting up any Windows compatibility items- I am running WinXP sp2, Intel dual core processor, nVidia 7950GX2 graphics card and Creative labs audio.

Please seed, I just hate to see old classics die out!
